New DELHI (AP)-Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin kafa kasa mai zuwa a watan gobe don gidan ibada na Hindu a wani yanki da ake takaddama a kansa a arewacin Indiya inda wasu masu tsattsauran ra'ayin Hindu suka rusa wani masallaci a karni na 16 a 1992, bisa ga amintar da ke kula ginin haikalin.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, ranar da masu shirya taron suka ce yana da matukar anfani ga mabiya addinin Hindu amma kuma hakan ya cika shekara guda kenan da Majalisar Dokokin Indiya ta soke matsayin ta mai cin gashin kai na jiharta daya da ke da rinjayen Musulmai, Jammu da Kashmir.
Alamar ba ta yiwu a rasa ba ga magoya baya da kuma masu hamayya da Modi ta dan kishin Hindu na Bharatiya Janata Party, ko BJP, wanda gabatarwar tasa ta kwashe shekaru da dama sun hada da alkawurran da suka yi na kwace ikon Kashmir na cin gashin kai da kuma gina gidan ibada ga gunkin Hindu Ram inda masallacin zamanin Mughal ya ke. Da zarar ya tsaya, wani wuri a cikin garin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh da masu ba da gaskiya suka yi imanin cewa mahaifar Ram ce.
Saboda kwayar cutar ta coronavirus tana ci gaba da yaduwa a duk fadin Indiya, wacce ta bayar da rahoto a karo na uku mafi girma a duniya, za a watsa bikin kai tsaye ta gidan talabijin din kasar kuma adadin mahalarta da 'yan kallo zai takaita, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kuma kungiyar Hindu na Duniya, kungiyar 'yan kishin Hindu da ke kawance da BJP.
Haikalin zai kasance a matsayin "cibiya mai dorewa da rashin dawwamammen hadin kai na zamantakewar al'umma, hadin kan kasa da hadewa da kuma farkawar jin ra'ayin Hindutva", ko hanyar rayuwar Hindu, in ji kakakin kungiyar Vinod Bansal a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Asabar.
